dc_title_s: Map of Michigan: compiled from the latest authentic sources.
dc_description_s: Shows counties, township and range lines. Shows major cities and towns. Shows "old state line". Cover title: Sectional Michigan. Accompanying index, 15 p. and list of cities with population of 10,000 and upward, [2] p. titled Page's indexed township map of Michigan ... Insets: Isle Royale.--[western portion of upper pennisula]. 1 map: col.; 86 x 59 cm., folded to 13 x 8 cm., in cover. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
